{"id":"ea53c9bf6cb9521e05032fe3ff95d9b3672430dcfafeda242c1a2887dc69aee8","item_id":"5b1b114ec2:0","text":"RenderMan for Blender 包含两种不同的降噪器：来自 Disney Research 的 RenderMan AI Denoiser（参见"}
{"id":"f6c88e6e9a8a21c9997f18f826f4020d77f403c445cd59b7c948b1ef5d5b2b0b","item_id":"5b1b114ec2:1","text":"Denoiser（降噪器）"}
{"id":"177e9e7313d9a35a7befb9504cec9f54646feced62d45acd2d6edafcacb47161","item_id":"5b1b114ec2:2","text":"）以及"}
{"id":"8b7ebce5534078becc3b4f43a8e3957f3daf0b3d257cf41703aa2acbb818598b","item_id":"5b1b114ec2:3","text":"Nvidia's AI Denoising（Nvidia AI 降噪）"}
{"id":"dfe707a9c8591694ebd599a625ab8531234cd6e75fa1bdf73813422d56bab9eb","item_id":"5b1b114ec2:4","text":"方案。"}
{"id":"1bce1bb1b07e34d3bd5684d118acd90f3c30d744a2797aa27dd75a9d1b790f0d","item_id":"5b1b114ec2:5","text":"Nvidia AI 降噪不适用于 macOS。"}
{"id":"efebd32a6ce38ec6fbc74948f9b5b59aaa0e0cef7670a7f1149681b86c08adae","item_id":"5b1b114ec2:6","text":"Interactive Rendering（交互式渲染）"}
{"id":"8143a04e78ced5d8c3c18bc6efafb51dc1b9779627dc89893ff4db6cfe429fd8","item_id":"5b1b114ec2:7","text":"有关在 \"it\" 中使用 Nvidia 降噪器的更多信息，请参阅"}
{"id":"16529ec5619a9c68ce445f90a1fd031478a10f57d667818b4a1f644d54a033e7","item_id":"5b1b114ec2:8","text":"Image Tool（图像工具）"}
{"id":"cdb4ee2aea69cc6a83331bbe96dc2caa9a299d21329efb0336fc02a82e1839a8","item_id":"5b1b114ec2:9","text":"中的 “AI Denoise” 小节。"}
{"id":"79637c3ab336308c0903b11e715ebc0622b4281fe003e36861f76aca7af2b368","item_id":"5b1b114ec2:10","text":"对于交互式渲染（viewport render、IPR 到 \"it\"），可以进入 viewport preferences（视口首选项），并在 IPR Denoiser 下选择一种降噪器来启用。Optix 指的是 Nvidia 降噪器。"}
{"id":"a977391d565a82d1c962ac70d47a1545b7090b911734876c3ad0bdb6645f08cc","item_id":"5b1b114ec2:11","text":"使用 Nvidia AI 降噪器时，应该会立即看到如下结果："}
{"id":"52e0e234aa2747932a2f36f169f4c3eac33cf1bb4967ee4681e66b02992b2cc4","item_id":"5b1b114ec2:12","text":"这是 RenderMan AI Denoiser 在两个 pass（遍）之后的结果："}
{"id":"9bcd8b880da2031a175a1d75ea0199ade207017f5baff05104cd0dc48295c598","item_id":"5b1b114ec2:13","text":"RenderMan AI Denoiser 还有一些额外控制项："}
{"id":"0fb29cc3c1247edb7c6bf6280a415aa95f39790f86b908b7565ed1be247ac249","item_id":"5b1b114ec2:14","text":"Cheap First Pass：如果勾选，第一次 denoise pass（降噪遍）会使用成本更低的启发式方法（稍快但质量较低）。如果渲染内容收敛很快，并且你希望优先更快得到降噪结果，这会很有用。"}
{"id":"0c5495e471e45186c2e94fe1594f6bc980e231bf7c4facfe15a2951827a37543","item_id":"5b1b114ec2:15","text":"Min Samples：交互式降噪首次运行前，每个 bucket（区块）所需的最小平均采样数。"}
{"id":"ae95436fb1d017f4e6d6882d17f53d4edb1ca594a5dac01198e71c7c98a31795","item_id":"5b1b114ec2:16","text":"Interval：两次降噪运行之间的时间间隔（秒）。"}
{"id":"ad86187e9d9e24899de162b5c8ec347252bbf422bfbce72ee79c5c9be1a9d7b3","item_id":"5b1b114ec2:17","text":"对于 preview renders（预览渲染，例如按 F12 或 Render→Render Image），如果渲染到 Blender 渲染窗口，可以在 Render Properties 选项卡中选择要使用的降噪器。"}
{"id":"5c632f081a8b5733d450228410c4a5a95321956444ded685023c8dd758cf6144","item_id":"5b1b114ec2:18","text":"对于 Nvidia AI 降噪器，应该会立即在渲染窗口中看到降噪后的结果。"}
{"id":"c7d99055e7f54da27f95f10ed5f123eeee3d9ea5bbc782c7759b1243f050e09a","item_id":"5b1b114ec2:19","text":"对于 RenderMan Denoiser，降噪器会在初始渲染完成后启动。渲染窗口中应该会出现一条消息，提示 denoising（降噪）已开始。"}
{"id":"4953c60f334471b57570572c8610c0ca1cdf699e11ca4cc138a7f3247922e38c","item_id":"5b1b114ec2:20","text":"这里是降噪后的最终结果（16 sample render，16 采样渲染）。"}
{"id":"d0db8b5e364b6989e4b8f38a2b3846b87d99a51c1592ebf35d21cc66405a8e39","item_id":"5b1b114ec2:21","text":"Options（选项）"}
{"id":"bc5c2028b8f8aeccae8cfc05e7e6d1ce379d207ff6153990bd24742c0e917bfa","item_id":"5b1b114ec2:22","text":"Use Color Pass"}
{"id":"b6e1d4dcd1fe098ea87e95c140ccdf26c68de38cc474c5ee58b8c32174e26069","item_id":"5b1b114ec2:23","text":"：未勾选时，beauty pass（beauty 通道）会通过合并已降噪的 diffuse pass 和 denoise specular pass 来完成降噪。这可以得到稍好一些的结果。不过，如果场景使用了任何 Display Filters 或 Sample Filters，可能会出现问题。遇到这种情况时，请勾选此框。"}
{"id":"a53793e93b8bda5f85aac863dc4b51947978d941da4dd1573122072bb0db1b99","item_id":"5b1b114ec2:24","text":"Asymmetry（不对称性）"}
{"id":"b768bca58708b9ca7beabe101aa5b28e374a73da1f9bd2ff32a036dd66bd9f81","item_id":"5b1b114ec2:25","text":"：控制 asymmetry（不对称性）值，0 表示最佳质量；较高值会促使降噪器避免过度模糊，从而产生较弱的降噪效果。"}
{"id":"d6b38a89dddc83b583c936ce451d5eec8a60e4e1df591f3f690a700b20393779","item_id":"5b1b114ec2:26","text":"Batch Rendering（批量渲染）"}
{"id":"385e56fac3ee4ed1f49e27fbce6f73d99d3e02b68f2c5aa50a2545a94bbf58d4","item_id":"5b1b114ec2:27","text":"有关 RenderMan for Blender 中 batch render（批量渲染）的更多通用信息，请参见"}
{"id":"5bd6cd38918929c15ad99bc4d31245659f7aed7cdbfb6923dc5ce378ced84f96","item_id":"5b1b114ec2:28","text":"Blender 中的批量渲染"}
{"id":"cdb4ee2aea69cc6a83331bbe96dc2caa9a299d21329efb0336fc02a82e1839a8","item_id":"5b1b114ec2:29","text":"。"}
{"id":"0e1e41bb2d1b47f6b54f46840f61cdda1a5da6d4143609513ff1a3850740c792","item_id":"5b1b114ec2:30","text":"请注意，如果使用 Blender Batch，并且启用了 Use Blender Compositor 选项，那么渲染属性选项卡中 Display 区段下的降噪器设置会被采用。"}
{"id":"f2be8551b2685b621a20c14ce194c055db2ba0e1f6be83555965191907645691","item_id":"5b1b114ec2:31","text":"如果使用 RIB batch render style（RIB 批量渲染样式），或关闭了 Use Blender Compositor，可以在 View Layer Properties 选项卡中启用降噪器。"}
{"id":"056fc3d37e92f2a9d390551dff6601dad412d3c03d5a5e49afc5a700ed1e7eb5","item_id":"5b1b114ec2:32","text":"在此批量渲染工作流中，只能使用 RenderMan Denoiser。Nvidia Optix 降噪器不是可用选项"}
{"id":"8eaa4b2f0da1f2da2bcb3e3e8065672a78e866346720be29354dc779beab7983","item_id":"5b1b114ec2:33","text":"你需要切换到 RenderMan Displays（有关在 Blender 中使用 AOV 的更多详细信息，"}
{"id":"dd5a5fbfa2ac4ce0dd81d2c459998a3643c8396e99a62075d84dfc47bd789184","item_id":"5b1b114ec2:34","text":"链接在这里！"}
{"id":"b221ad9c7759a03dd389e513594b096101d1edab3f93872ce59e99aa373ef875","item_id":"5b1b114ec2:35","text":"前往 View Layer Properties 并点击"}
{"id":"babaa43c84899a23abf44759da6b288f3a3c30e5a3b6bcbdeb84510b1f16968d","item_id":"5b1b114ec2:36","text":"Switch to RenderMan Displays"}
{"id":"1ef0d1204dfc8b0707634dcc486fdf1ad80bd399bb62c25e63515558b6b105e2","item_id":"5b1b114ec2:37","text":"在 RenderMan Display 中，选择 beauty AOV 并启用"}
{"id":"f6a472cd40532137ebfcb05358ce32a433f343a156a30519b7fa5bb85a014d68","item_id":"5b1b114ec2:38","text":"Denoise（降噪）"}
{"id":"2f421a68bc6fe43a3729bdd4b090726c0834f1aed66815819addaa0c547c5a05","item_id":"5b1b114ec2:39","text":"设置所需的降噪器参数，就可以开始了。"}
